name: MyDinnerApp
0:
”Alexa, ask dinner suggestions what's for dinner?”
”Where should I go for dinner?”
”Where should we go for dinner?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dinner suggestions
des: Ask Alexa "What's for dinner?", and she will respond with an option from a long list of potential winners. Great when you can't decide what you or your family/friends should have for dinner!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
